{"id": 124, "genre": 1000, "title": "你最不反感的广告是什么样的？", "description": "人人都烦广告？大概是这样的。但在这个消费世界里，所有的间隙都已经被广告占满啦，目之所及的美女都出现在广告里，付出真情地看一篇文章结果发现是软文……你讨厌这样嘛？\r\n", "record_count": 2569, "comment_count": 39, "praise_count": 0, "image": "img/paper/paper_show/20160607194145v4ReHimq53uGtahb.jpg", "page_style": 0, "category": 1, "column": 2, "type": "paper", "date": "2014-10-30T08:46:24Z", "questions": [{"id": 113, "title": "你最不反感的广告是什么样的？", "content": "你最不反感的广告是什么样的？\r\n", "genre": 1, "options": [{"id": 965, "content": "形式或者内容有创意的视频或者电视广告", "image": "img/option/option/20160607192530eThunW13pPof6BSa.gif", "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0}, {"id": 966, "content": "有我喜欢的明星或者赏心悦目的代言人的广告", "image": "img/option/option/20160607192530E7hKIcsCkurnd4Yy.jpg", "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0}, {"id": 967, "content": "段子手苦心经营的内嵌在段子里的广告", "image": "img/option/option/20160607192530A6tzlXNi7bRVg9HW.jpg", "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0}, {"id": 968, "content": "大V（貌似）亲身试过的产品或者馆子的广告", "image": "img/option/option/20160607192530GlFfUWMRbkXBPTyc.jpeg", "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0}, {"id": 969, "content": "互动可以减价或者赢奖品的广告", "image": "img/option/option/20160607192530Li6fnsqMbT94ABGW.jpg", "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0}, {"id": 970, "content": "电影里意识不到的广告植入", "image": "img/option/option/20160607192530mKRkVaq8I2OXUDv9.jpg", "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0}, {"id": 971, "content": "豆瓣边栏里那种清新的广告", "image": "img/option/option/20160607192529ol4U269Ln7bP31Nu.png", "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0}]}]}